name: BodeGato #001 Name:Cake
description: Wow! Looks like you found a Bodegato! We call her Cake and she’s a real sweetheart, not like Ónix.. that cat’s crazy!   The CARIBverse is full of this cute little ones, well of course! they love fresh fish and some occasional attention in their own terms. Some of them are strays, others have a family (or 2) and a lot of them hang around the uh!Bodega because they know we’ll feed them nice treats.   Stay around and try to collect them all. Meooooow!
